# Greenhouse company slugs — EXAMPLE
# Copy this file to config/feed_urls.txt and replace with your target companies.
# Format: one slug per line. The slug is the company identifier in Greenhouse's API.
# The pipeline calls: boards-api.greenhouse.io/v1/boards/{slug}/jobs?content=true
#
# To find a company's slug: look at their jobs page URL, e.g.
#   https://boards.greenhouse.io/openai  →  slug is "openai"
#
# Validate each slug works before adding: curl that URL and check for a jobs list.

openai
anthropic
coreweave
google
